res. It might still be an issue, so I should inspect the supervisor's instructions for any ACP-specific mechanisms that could be involved. There are some components to ensue I should clarify on this. I’m just making sure everything is processed correctly!\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4jJ3NBwQNOyIhZQ67885GYZZ|fc_09720d3158cc1b3e0169cffb472c08819188c41c1239365844","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\OPERATIONS.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\\\OPERATIONS.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0J2qIdD6LkqZN09RD2ThGwqK|fc_09720d3158cc1b3e0169cffb472c14819185a3d3de75789566","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\MISSION.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\\\MISSION.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_zfiCDX8TYLIDSDFL288bK0an|fc_09720d3158cc1b3e0169cffb472c188191a52d9c93a9efeadf","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\agents\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\CONTRACT.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\sm_s3_visual_planning\\\\CONTRACT.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1457,"output":161,"cacheRead":28672,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30290,"cost":{"input":0.0036425000000000003,"output":0.002415,"cacheRead":0.007168,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.013225500000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775237954726,"responseId":"resp_09720d3158cc1b3e0169cffb4311888191a30450150869d55d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"76207ffd","parentId":"75256182","timestamp":"2026-04-03T17:39:19.140Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4jJ3NBwQNOyIhZQ67885GYZZ|fc_09720d3158cc1b3e0169cffb472c08819188c41c1239365844","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# OPERATIONS.md\n\n## Regras operacionais\n\n1. Contexto limpo por activação.\n2. Estado no disco > conversa.\n3. Falha explícita > sucesso ambíguo.\n4. Não inventar outputs inexistentes.\n5. Não considerar um operator concluído apenas por resposta textual.\n\n## Sequência base\n\n1. Validar bootstrap.\n2. Escrever checkpoint de supervisor started.\n3. Resolver activation plan.\n4. Ler `operator_registry.md`.\n5. Gerar payloads de dispatch compatíveis com `s3.operator_dispatch.v1`.\n6. Invocar operators activos.\n7. Monitorizar `status.json`, `checkpoint.json` e `output.json` por operator.\n8. Validar outputs estruturais.\n9. Fazer retry selectivo quando permitido.\n10. Compilar `compiled_entities.json`.\n11. Gerar `s3_sector_report.md`.\n12. Escrever checkpoint final.\n\n## Limites\n\n- não és boundary Paperclip-facing\n- não és o `b2_director`\n- não deves delegar compile final para os operators\n- não deves chamar operators fora do registry oficial\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775237959133}}
{"type":"message","id":"7d6b59ea","parentId":"76207ffd","timestamp":"2026-04-03T17:39:19.153Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0J2qIdD6LkqZN09RD2ThGwqK|fc_09720d3158cc1b3e0169cffb472c14819185a3d3de75789566","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MISSION.md\n\nA tua missão é assumir o controlo operativo do sector S3 para um único job, com contexto limpo por activação.\n\nDeves:\n- validar o bootstrap recebido\n- assumir formalmente o sector\n- resolver o activation plan\n- preparar dispatch payloads dos operators\n- invocar os operators certos\n- monitorizar outputs por artefactos persistidos\n- validar outputs estruturais\n- compilar `compiled_entities.json`\n- gerar `s3_sector_report.md`\n- escrever checkpoint final de sucesso, degradação ou falha\n\nNunca deves depender de memória conversacional residual.\nO disco é a fonte de verdade.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775237959140}}
{"type":"message","id":"c82e94ba","parentId":"7d6b59ea","timestamp":"2026-04-03T17:39:19.162Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_zfiCDX8TYLIDSDFL288bK0an|fc_09720d3158cc1b3e0169cffb472c188191a52d9c93a9efeadf","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# CONTRACT.md\n\n## Bootstrap input\nLês um payload compatível com `s3.supervisor_bootstrap.v1`.\n\nCampos obrigatórios:\n- `kind = s3_start`\n- `contract_version`\n- `job_id`\n- `video_id`\n- `account_id`\n- `language`\n- `run_root`\n- `sector_root`\n- `source_package_path`\n- `checkpoints_dir`\n- `operators_dir`\n- `compiled_dir`\n- `logs_dir`\n- `dispatch_dir`\n- `bootstrap_checkpoint_path`\n\n## Outputs obrigatórios\n- artefacto de arranque do supervisor\n- `operator_activation_plan.json`\n- payloads de dispatch dos operators activos\n- snapshots/artefactos de monitorização e validação\n- `compiled/compiled_entities.json`\n- `compiled/s3_sector_report.md`\n- `checkpoints/s3_sector_completed.json` ou `checkpoints/s3_sector_failed.json`\n\n## Success rule\nSó fechas o sector como concluído quando os artefactos finais existirem e estiverem estruturalmente coerentes.\n\n## Failure rule\nSe faltar precondição crítica, falha explicitamente e persiste o checkpoint de falha.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775237959154}}
{"type":"message","id":"757bbee5","parentId":"c82e94ba","timestamp":"2026-04-03T17:39:25.821Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Inspecting agent sessions**\n\nI need to run some real invocation with the exec and openclaw agent. It might be useful to check sessions and logs or inspect artifacts. I think using the new run_007 could help. I should also search for the ACP runtime message in the agent session. It’s probably a good idea to inspect the existing run_005 files and the session log to get more insights. Let’s take a look!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_09720d3158cc1b3e0169cffb4814fc8191a1264ace0c0f930b\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpz_tLoTLnWz6WgOrsJi_r-GmuF4g4DA7WBH-lQUwoigfp6SuBtpxmrphEQfxjoHlv7t_ErY0uU3Qg2-tte6aghwLsxzaasnUUY6taw6sXVOEYWXtWV4eUPI6m4qBDGEvQ3jQT4pUgOQzeO4SMgYijELB_P9iMnTaeufi_o_RW2NuaAwTKXrczX0wuegWP5nnLONisjqsWuPFrBWwcO_McuM6-x1P44mgFRNsv7cV8nSXJ-10Kl88kIX3wfz3H-dwn594LPQnOBq0GTBI9CenApT5gv4I_CyC-c1lKe5NEZ2Yujm1i_s73sfvO3K0S58enPnHCBoRFbA74j2WQZU0RIiC8pUKI9b0HXpJ0oCDU4j7C_WVCvshtE1ncIwRAMlUY_wb0VTxvhfKTHvD8T1thGhiRoyqjML9qtAyEcQ_1PzxhS6xsc1y6BrI3h5zn8D406yN1EohGDy-yYHtEqbOhGrKqfbaqVQA77aaoQ1nySqK0rIaM5xkNKmu1fTUKhsCrTtAzVhXXp1UoB-DmsyqwKdraDfAU5dS1kRDGzhQLim8WJeZcZIFXou5UVQVGrEyUiPkIWm8Fuagr3Urnehffp_k_FquUhTFhB3Vs87eOij9CKTByJ-E5iXMC4CMVWk_4UgWlQhfWbb0vYBzyl5LV-VHIkDjoLfqE0B5jjX16cE_kJHtX2E7PQQmgaTu6nn_-O-r3RFc-FKbkTxYA3KeB9t-R-PeO-EkwEk0MQA-Q2p0curKA-_QIwHzB2selnD4nfa7gjCgInLMLhY8PZGedlVOZzXrG62kq4Gpp40T_RhaFktkZum1QsNv7z9sQ6TM3BTPWOIfVubqkOVlKU6e34An2CBnKsUYF-jY-DlREP56eG095rvusaYv2z4z_j59bKuqgrsF7JhQh8ZkU6iw6GlSOWXzBsc0hwIPNtSENfKEGyqoyQZRNBLf1SlPcFL1ZETAjDdZ6cVitY9gNmfrbYMCEu5lSVa-mfgqi0FhZriIbbHchsboKfdlPDjZ0U6raWJXpolKWkuNCsbmYrbeWerh99TnKiqr_AzmIOyLAZQ73Du42FxvpX1fEnyQymhghmFgSiOBv4MYipLQ1iWHooYwmFfFPCjV_JhufsL3XILHLvNpGMQdt4aI0Cileshy5ueiwIBQQ3Ev30fSEVK924Q5pzA==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Inspecting agent sessions**\\n\\nI need to run